name: AM&J Marketing Network Professionals
overview:
AM&J does NOT participate in MLM (multi-level-marketing) in any way. AM&J professionals are B2C (business-to-client) relationship developers. AM&J creates, manages, and supports all levels of marketing networks. AM&J supports current market networks and provides essential solutions that are cost effective. AM&J professionals are available to answer any questions and offer solutions for promoting, marketing, and networking any size business.

Providing services, included but not limited to:

*email account setup

*Interent visibility

*marketing strategies and management

*multi-network account setup and support

*network/marketing assessment (FREE)

*virtual communication

*website development solutions

….and much more
